                        <interp inst="t18391021-name-140" type="given" value="ARTHUR THOMAS"></interp>ARTHUR THOMAS KILBY</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a policeman. I searched him, and found the property on him.</p>
               <p>(<hi rend="italic">The prisoner put in a written defence, stating that he had found the twist near Covent-garden, but as it was not the sort he required, he still vent to the prosecutor's to purchase</hi>.)</p>
